
Storage standards {{{1

PATA	parallel ATA, i.e. IDE

SATA - serial ATA
	current standard for new controllers

AHCI SATA - Advanced Host Controller Interface
	devices appear as PCI?

libata
	merge of PATA support
	as of 2.6.19, drivers in kernel under: 
		"Device drivers -> Serial ATA (prod) and Parallel ATA (experimental) drivers")
	legacy PATA drivers under:
		"Device drivers -> ATA/ATAPI/MFM/RLL support"

